description:
Just in case you don't like vlogs:

1. In the charity we did a few weeks back, Spreadshirt got back to me and we raised $2340 JUST in T-shirt sales. Meaning, we raised a grand total of $9630 for our Save The Children campaign. INCREDIBLE WORK MY SAMURAI BRETHREN.

2. A year ago I couldn't even afford to go to Pax East by myself, and now just a short year later I'm able to not only fund my trip, but help out with financial probs going on in my family -- thanks to you guys' support on the channel.

3. HUGE thanks to my good friend Tear Of Grace (https://www.youtube.com/user/TearofGrace) for helping out handsomely during the charity and just being a good dude in general. Also s/o to the Emily Wants To Play dev for stopping by the stream and showing so much love.

4. I love you Samurai to death, you all make me so extremely happy everyday and I am so blessed to belong to a community like this one.

Top outro video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9KNFVS-jqk
Bottom outro video:  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DaVoUU0KO5E
